headline: Homes.com Report: Home Prices Rise in February, but at a Slower Rate than the Previous Two Months
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., March 07, 2025--Homes.com, a CoStar Group leading online residential marketplace, today released a new report looking at housing prices for the month of February based on information collected to date. The preliminary analysis yielded key insights on home prices, which are still rising but at a slower rate than previous months, what the price growth moderation means for homebuyers, and what regions of the country the highest price appreciation rates are coming from.
